{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t14-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数的运算","title":"针对训练1：绝对值综合运算","difficulty":4,"tags":["绝对值","分类讨论"],"content":"若 $|a| = 5$，$|b| = 7$，$|a + b| = a + b$，则 $a - b = $ ______。","steps":[{"title":"分析条件","content":"$|a + b| = a + b$ 说明 $a + b \\geq 0$\n\n$|a| = 5 \\Rightarrow a = 5$ 或 $a = -5$\n$|b| = 7 \\Rightarrow b = 7$ 或 $b = -7$","formula":""},{"title":"分类讨论","content":"满足 $a + b \\geq 0$ 的组合：\n• $a = 5, b = 7$：$a + b = 12 \\geq 0$ ✓，$a - b = -2$\n• $a = 5, b = -7$：$a + b = -2 < 0$ ✗\n• $a = -5, b = 7$：$a + b = 2 \\geq 0$ ✓，$a - b = -12$\n• $a = -5, b = -7$：$a + b = -12 < 0$ ✗","formula":"\\text{答案：}-2 \\text{ 或 } -12"}]},"id":"t14-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}